&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Strike&#39;s mission is to build a more connected financial world.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strike allows users to send and receive money anywhere, instantly, with no fees.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strike is built on top of the Bitcoin network - the largest global, interoperable and open payments standard. Strike believes that open payment networks enable universal participation in the financial system, ushering in a new digital economy with truly borderless money transfers. Strike leverages Bitcoin’s open payment network to offer users the first global peer-to-peer payments app and a novel bitcoin-native neobanking experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Role:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;As a key member of our QA team, you’ll directly impact the lifeline of the business by maintaining a high bar for quality of our top rated iOS, Android and Web apps. You’ll own major features, working closely with different disciplines across the company.&lt;br&gt;We’re looking for an engineer that will grow with the company and is excited about Strike’s mission and potential. The person joining us must be comfortable with a team-first approach in a remote work environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building test plans for new features and improving existing test plans for feature updates and customer feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Executing tests on our release candidates for iOS, Android and Web apps&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Owning features through inception, design feedback, implementation, and launch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with Product Designers, Product Managers, Backend Engineers, and Customer Support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Requirements:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience developing software using C#, JavaScript, React&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with automated test tools including TestCafé, Testing Library, Selenium, Waldo, xUnit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with API tools including Swagger, Postman, Proxyman&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and passion for tough technical problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attention to detail and voice of customer experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience automating end to end UI tests for iOS, Android and Web clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with cross-functional teams in fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Additional Qualifications:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with consumer centric app testing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong sense of quality, product intuition and user empathy&lt;/li&gt;
