&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking for experienced software engineers from a variety of technical backgrounds with a proven track record in building scalable, reliable and performant systems. You will play a critical role in evolving the core platforms which drive our retail products. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As an engineer in the Card Issuing team, you will be responsible for a key part of the Blockchain.com roadmap. Issuing cards to our customers will help us bring Blockchain.com’s products further in the daily lives of our users. Looking after their spendings requires a great amount of care and our mission is to design, build, and maintain reliable systems that ensure broad access and efficient payments for all our customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
